headline.print_headline: One in Eight Adults in the City Has Diabetes, a Study Finds
headline.main: One in Eight Adults in the City Has Diabetes, a Study Finds

docs.lead_paragraph: The study shows that almost one-third of those who have diabetes are unaware of it, as are many of those with prediabetes, or abnormally high blood sugar.
